{"tid":1367503,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"1972 太古地產","createTime":"2019-07-26T09:30:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T04:21:39.000Z","uid":81368,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"7ee0b623272d339cf208dc004a9267d107f5f796","tid":1367503,"uid":81368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T09:30:44.000Z","msg":"好好地俾大行唱幾野就跌，佢老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n均價29.8，持貨兩年<br />\n係咪應該換第二隻"},{"pid":"feb86d2846bc00a20df2961e1d991f2fbd59be65","tid":1367503,"uid":181639,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T09:40:23.000Z","msg":"佢未來除咗太古坊二期同上海前灘，都無乜其他大project<br />\nCitygate extension都喺得20%喺屬於佢<br />\n而加開始喺印尼起樓都要時間去收成<br />\n加上預計租金收益下降<br />\n見唔到好大增長動力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過佢啲資產喺好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e99697e3f12378df003e5f0eaf156b235747b02a","tid":1367503,"uid":246729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T09:55:45.000Z","msg":"愛股<br />\n物業優質，寫字樓 商場 酒店 加少少住宅發展<br />\n嚟緊除左 太古坊二期，仲有 鰂魚涌海X街重建<br />\n行過少少 有 仁孚 兩幢重建<br />\n之後灣仔都有個重建項目<br />\n今年東涌新翼開幕，開始有新收入<br />\n仲有內地&amp;美國 有新Project / 就快有野起好<br />\n<br />\n比大行唱淡，主因係估值高過 過去五年嘅高位(高好多)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自己就睇息率入貨，股市估唔到市，高處可以再高"},{"pid":"82963271bcb94814c62f30475422f5acc801f96d","tid":1367503,"uid":193290,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:56:35.000Z","msg":"87有貨"},{"pid":"71d1c9e89ae9517b4cae2671b504ad72c192e0a3","tid":1367503,"uid":34013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:27:42.000Z","msg":"睇好佢同中巴有幾塊地合作起樓 唔知幾時賣<br />\nBUT中巴穩陣好多   $97入左幾手 陰下陰下升到$128又唔識跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"476aa966bf876f5e8f47002846f82fc1bee8202c","tid":13